  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: General </p><p>Prerequisite: Proficiency in either Ninshou or Martial Arts, Level 4+ </p><p>You specialize in the art of Clashing, gaining the following benefits; </p><p>• Choose between Ninshou or Martial Arts.</p><p> When you participate in a Jutsu Clash, treat your ranks of Mastery in your chosen skill as +1 higher, so long as you are proficient with the skill.</p><p>• You can always tell if a Jutsu possesses the Clash keyword just from seeing it cast.</p><p>• You do not become Dazed as the result of losing a Clash.</p><p>• When you succeed a Jutsu Clash, you can choose to knock the target back 30 feet.</p><p>• Select two jutsu that you know.</p><p> These jutsu become known as your Clashing Jutsu.</p><p> You may change which jutsu are your Clashing Jutsu on a long rest.</p><p> Your Clashing Jutsu gain the Clash keyword, and once per rest you may cast these jutsu as a Reaction to being targeted by a Jutsu or Effect with the Clash keyword, ignoring the listed casting time.</p><p></p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
